channel.title: Packet help
channel.description:
Hey, obviously ive done something wrong and keep getting this error and everyone will dc. Ive looked around for a few hours and cant seem to find a problem. I figured i might aswell post on here while i keep searching around.
[IMG]http://img380.imageshack.us/img380/7803/errorsjamesij5.jpg[/img]
If anyone can help THANKYOU SwiftY

item.title: Packet help
item.dc:creator: @Yz85Racer Yz85Racer
item.description:
@Yz85Racer wrote:

By the looks of it, it can mean a few things:
- It could be behind a firewall, not allowing any incoming<->outgoing data.
- You could be reading the packet prematurely?

Read full topic
